<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="post_list_content_unit">
<h2 class="post_list_item_title"><a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/churchill-lewis-carroll/" title="View full">Churchill as a Character from the Works of Lewis Carroll</a></h2>
<div class="post_list_meta_unit">
<div class="date-d">21</div>
<div class="date-m">Sep</div>
<div class="date-y">2023</div>
</div>
<div class="post_list_inner_content_unit post_list_inner_content_unit_left">
<div class="authorlooplist">By <span>GARY L. STILES</span></div>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/churchill-lewis-carroll/" title="Read more about Churchill as a Character from the Works of Lewis Carroll">
<div class="post_list_featured_image">
<img width="770" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-lazy-type="image" data-lazy-src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/0Tenniel-770x300.jpg" class="lazy lazy-hidden img-responsive wp-post-image" alt decoding="async" /><noscript><img width="770" height="300" src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/0Tenniel-770x300.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" /></noscript> </div>
</a>
<div class="post_list_item_excerpt">Churchill was represented as a character from Lewis Carroll eight times: a wide range, from the innocent Alice to the bizarre Mad Hatter to the supercilious Caterpillar. Whatever their politics, the cartoons were devoid of viciousness, suggesting the affection in which he was held, often by those who utter disagreed with him. They are artefacts of a vanished political age. </div>

<div class="post_list_cats">
<span class="post_list_cats_label">Posted in:</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/category/explore-articles/">Explore</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/category/explore-articles/the-literary-churchill/">The Literary Churchill</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
</div>

<div class="post_list_item_tags">
<span class="post_list_tags_label">Tags:</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/tag/alice-in-wonderland/">Alice in Wonderland</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/tag/gary-stiles/">Gary Stiles</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/tag/lewis-carroll/">Lewis Carroll</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/tag/winston-s-churchill/">Winston S. Churchill</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
