<div class="post_list_content_unit">
<h2 class="post_list_item_title"><a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/austen-neville-chamberlain/" title="View full">Band of Brothers: Austen and Neville Chamberlain, and Their Eulogists</a></h2>
<div class="post_list_meta_unit">
<div class="date-d">16</div>
<div class="date-m">Jun</div>
<div class="date-y">2022</div>
</div>
<div class="post_list_inner_content_unit post_list_inner_content_unit_left">
<div class="authorlooplist">By <span>DAVE TURRELL</span></div>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/austen-neville-chamberlain/" title="Read more about Band of Brothers: Austen and Neville Chamberlain, and Their Eulogists">
<div class="post_list_featured_image">
<img width="770" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-lazy-type="image" data-lazy-src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/29Sep38-770x300.jpg" class="lazy lazy-hidden img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Chamberlain" decoding="async" loading="lazy" /><noscript><img width="770" height="300" src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/29Sep38-770x300.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Chamberlain" decoding="async" loading="lazy" /></noscript> </div>
</a>
<div class="post_list_item_excerpt">All are all now firmly established in the great pantheon of the House of Commons. All experienced failure, engendered controversy, still do, and always will. In death, all passion spent, they can be evaluated for the characters that lay beneath their politics. And, in common, a deep seam of basic decency can be found.</div>

